{"tid":1598092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本防衛大臣：中國已取代朝鮮 成為日本的最大威脅","createTime":"2019-09-27T09:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:09:24.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"55891c810acfe93e59ff5bdfbd9eef858c3b90f7","tid":1598092,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d8d987c2e39591811a8c2b4.jpg/D5HhhgT6Rz-hspFEWOoIUKV4cm6_tPrzOX0jWzl9I1s?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d8d987c2e39591811a8c2b4.jpg%2FD5HhhgT6Rz-hspFEWOoIUKV4cm6_tPrzOX0jWzl9I1s%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=372f601f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d8d986cda2377195855b833.jpg/uhvXy-VXe3ofbzF2ggVn88_nqjVDAlmaTY2Y6E2NmOg?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d8d986cda2377195855b833.jpg%2FuhvXy-VXe3ofbzF2ggVn88_nqjVDAlmaTY2Y6E2NmOg%3Fv%3Dw960&h=0b72add7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本在9月27日發布的《防衛白皮書》中指出，中國對日本的威脅，比擁有核武的朝鮮為大。圖為朝鮮政府8月24日對外發布的照片，可見當局在一個沒有公開位置的地點測試型號不明的導彈。（AP）<br />\n<br />\n美國被列於《防衛白皮書》第一部份，中國則取代朝鮮，列於第二部份。一向被日本政府視為最大威脅的朝鮮，列於第三部份。俄羅斯被放在第四部份。<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛大臣河野太郎在記者會上就這個安排表示：「現實是中國在快速增加軍事開支，所以人們可以理解，我們（在這方面需要）更多篇幅。」他說：「中國在西太平洋部署空中和海上資產，以及頻繁地通過對馬海峽進入日本海（韓稱東海）。」<br />\n<br />\n此外在《防衞白皮書》內名為「安全保障合作」章節中，韓國的排序從2018版中第二降至第四。日本國防部消息人士解釋道，這實際上是將韓國的重要性降級。<br />\n<br />\n韓國在2018年白皮書中在「準同盟國」排名第二，僅次於澳洲。韓國在2019年版的《防衞白皮書》中排在澳洲、印度和東盟之後的第四位。這排序被認為反映各國之於日本的重要程度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/380008/日本-防衞白皮書-指中國威脅比朝鮮大\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F380008%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9E%E7%99%BD%E7%9A%AE%E6%9B%B8-%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E6%AF%94%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E5%A4%A7&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=b9e3c8b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/380008/日本-防衞白皮書-指中國威脅比朝鮮大</a>"},{"pid":"8cd0502e05390dd8a1bb7b9a9d6dadafe6ce2ae9","tid":1598092,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"中國復仇主義"},{"pid":"ddd9699ab0b38f11a7f7c7a3dc37330cddff35a6","tid":1598092,"uid":318838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:21:17.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國幾時復活打支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef81e1e7c2a2d3dcb397ac1b0fc63b9e48dd3614","tid":1598092,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"又多個反支猛員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8161ef313494067d99a23c881f168e1cd0e3d8d3","tid":1598092,"uid":194325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=8c2f9c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=b55cbc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcHaJTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcHaJTs.jpg&h=032e94ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWfr1E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWfr1E9.jpg&h=defd0334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdP4Oj9.jp